$title[0] 	= "Rank: Provost";
$banner[0] 	= "<img src=\"../images/banner_provost.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\"/>";
$rnk_p11[0]	= "The <b>provost</b>, for all intent and purposes, within the context of the Academy, is the Academy's <b>maestro</b> or <b>master</b>.  Without a formal title of <b>maestro</b> conveyed to the provost by the an existing <b>master</b> of the art, the provost cannot use the title of maestro or master externally to the Academy.";
$rnk_p12[0]	= "First and foremost, the <b>provost</b> must have a proven track record in the instruction of the art, and is skilled in all weapons as described by Fiore dei Liberi's treatise.  The <b>provost</b> has developed an intimate understanding of the different characteristics, underlying principles and theoretical approaches to each of the weapons and fighting styles described.  This individual has obtained this rank after a minimum of eight (8) years of study and training.  Key responsibilities of the <b>provost</b> is the training and teaching of students, and the contribution to the general operations and/or administration functions of the Academy.  An official teaching license or letter is granted by the Academy governing body to those who have successfully prized at this rank.";
$rnk_p13[0]	= "The <b>provost</b> also must abide by the rules, similar to those rules of the <b>maestro</b> which describes ones responsibilities of this rank, which includes stating one's allegiance and loyalties to the organization (in this case, to the Academy), and an all-encompassing code of conduct and behaviour which the <b>provost</b> is expected to abide by within the context of historical martial arts.  The <b>provost</b> must abide by the rules and constitution of the Academy, and promote the principles of historical martial arts and organizations that are focused on the formalization of these arts.";

$title_p2[0] 	= "Provost Requirements";
$rnk_l21[0]	= "\"time in\" as free scholler of a minimum of five (5) years,";
$rnk_l22[0]	= "demonstrated teaching skill in both individually-oriented training and group-oriented training sessions,";
$rnk_l23[0]	= "has delivered instruction to regularly scheduled classes,";
$rnk_l24[0]	= "possesses a solid analytical understanding of the historical treatises relevant to the art of <i>armizare</i>,";
$rnk_l25[0]	= "possesses skill in multiple weapons as described in Fiore dei Liberi's treatise,";
$rnk_l26[0]	= "earned a minimum of level 1 <a href=\"http://www.coach.ca/coach-training-in-canada-s15408\" target=\"_blank\"><b>NCCP</b></a> certification,";
$rnk_l27[0]	= "title of <b>provost</b> conveyed by the Academy's governing body,";
$rnk_l28[0]	= "the <b>provost</b> candidate has been assessed and observed by the Academy's senior members and executive through time of the candidate's abilities with respect to all aspects of <b>armizare</b> as described by Fiore dei Liberi, and most importantly, their instruction and teaching capabilities,";
$rnk_l29[0]	= "must be of at least 30 years of age,";
$rnk_l210[0]	= "the candidate is considered if the following are satisfied:";
$rnk_l211[0]	= "demonstrated knowledge of fencing & fight theory by responding to queries by the Academy's governing body or by his/her peers,";
$rnk_l212[0]	= "demonstrated teaching skill by giving an individual lesson(s) and group lesson(s) to the other candidates or students identified by the Academy's senior members and governing body,";
$rnk_l213[0]	= "demonstrated fencing and fighting proficiency in the art of <i>armizare</i>,";
$rnk_l214[0]	= "demonstrated knowledge of hopology by analysis of a weapon chosen randomly by the Academy's governing body or by his/her peers,";
$rnk_l215[0]	= "formally makes the request to the governing body of his/her intention for the rank of <b>provost</b>.";
$rnk_l216[0]	= "has submitted at least one or more research papers submission to the Academy's governing body, its review and acceptance.";
$rnk_l217[0]	= "is prepared to participate in the Academy's governing body.";

